Body:
Greetings YPOers!

Last chance for those of you who have not signed up for this upcoming YPO
Fly Away of a lifetime.

In case you forgot what your missing here is a recap of events:
Dinner at Palace Cafe
Brunch at Commander's Palace
Ride on the Krewe of Orpheus float in full costume.
Party at Krewe of Orpheus Ball and lots of more surprises!

Cost per rider is $3,300.00 per person.  Spouses are welcome to ride too!

You have until July 1st to respond and then it is open to WPOers!

The dates again are February 10 - 12, 2002.

Please contact Kay-La Hughes at 713-522-9223 ext. 310 to sign up!

Les Bon Temps Rouler!

